<img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//95b4/95b4cda22ba385adf2e750cb8a90d5df.com/large/19960008dd42ef51045d"> 
<p>Sergei觉得，这样别出心裁的照顾孩子，大概是一件他10年后想起来，都会无比自豪的事！</p> 
<img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//e496/e496acd3144a62741657a8d7b70e7f31.com/large/199a0008e210e9a64cfd"> 
